        "Score each technology against requirements",
        "Rank technologies for application",
        "Generate comparison report"
      ],
      "expectedOutput": "Memory technology comparison tool",
      "hints": [
        "Coherence critical for storage time",
        "Telecom wavelength for fiber networks",
        "Efficiency affects key rate",
        "Temperature affects deployment cost"
      ]
    },
