        "Calculate effective rates with multiplexing",
        "Compare g²(0) for source quality",
        "Analyze trade-offs (rate vs purity)",
        "Recommend source for use case"
      ],
      "expectedOutput": "Photon source selection system",
      "hints": [
        "g²(0) < 1 indicates quantum source",
        "Multiplexing improves effective rate",
        "Deterministic sources simpler for protocols",
        "Consider wavelength matching needs"
      ]
